{"tid":1314304,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[因為係白衫追打] 員佐級協會澄清上水衝突警員無追打示威者","createTime":"2019-07-14T06:14:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-14T06:53:14.000Z","uid":70782,"like":61,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"3bb765257d4ce02daaddfe71d72bcc7d4f395ea5","tid":1314304,"uid":70782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T06:14:57.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】警察隊員佐級協會發公開信，澄清上水衝突期間，警員並無追打示威者，以致對方要跳橋逃走。<br />\n<br />\n協會說，從電視台片段可見，警方在行人天橋清場期間，有示威者跨越天橋圍欄企圖離開，幸而幾名警察趕至將他拉回，安全返到橋面。<br />\n<br />\n協會指，立法會議員尹兆堅言之鑿鑿稱，是警察追打示威者，令他要跳橋逃走，是捏造事實、誤導公眾、行為卑劣，譴責有人明目張膽扭曲事實。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=355357\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D355357&d=05%2BDYq1PAX1syIB%2FutXPapugP7yqsTcUQnBN8ZzcBqk%3D&h=7f5b5736\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D355357&h=32fab2ef\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=355357</a><br />\n<br />\n散仔福利部又出公開信, 今次割返佢上司蓆<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fca70600e3658fa6d758fa56ffdd01b35e0ad0c","tid":1314304,"uid":50457,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T06:16:59.000Z","msg":"福利會又發表政治言論<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />